{"tid":987510,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道，三月尾四月頭有咩好玩","createTime":"2019-01-19T11:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T13:50:38.000Z","uid":57306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef012826e0fcc84620a629397693ea90ea3f951a","tid":987510,"uid":57306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"27/3-3/4<br />\n花海雪祭冇<br />\n破冰船又冇<br />\n就連道東三湖個架巴士都唔開<br />\nr 爆頭都諗唔到點plan<br />\n唔通真係要成個星期留係札幌<br />\n我都係想睇下自然景姐<br />\n唔怪得機票咁撚平<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲，有冇好推介<br />\n登別 洞爺 函館已經去過<br />\n一條友 非自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab92cb9541ecce3d480a540c1219d7261ce9692","tid":987510,"uid":108236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"屌閪！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5633d1b7b8871f7229cb1a6f3012894040f3dc04","tid":987510,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"求撚其啦你。"},{"pid":"e9569137964295df3413895cb5d495bab44620ab","tid":987510,"uid":52036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"去薄野"},{"pid":"cf35d71b4edfd3a36de36a923797e5b3f9c03e98","tid":987510,"uid":138316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"呢個時期係北海道旅遊淡季<br />\n需然好似冇咩睇，但勝在少d遊客唔駛同人爭<br />\n去美瑛踩單車好涼爽望住個雪山景<br />\n另外想滑雪可以上旭岳"},{"pid":"c531ee6b8c2e31fec3dcd8835cc15c241258d8b0","tid":987510,"uid":57306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf35d71b4edfd3a36de36a923797e5b3f9c03e98","tid":987510,"uid":138316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"呢個時期係北海道旅遊淡季<br />\n需然好似冇咩睇，但勝在少d遊客唔駛同人爭<br />\n去美瑛踩單車好涼爽望住個雪山景<br />\n另外想滑雪可以上旭岳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"我就唔識滑雪踩單車ge<b